{"title_page": "Alejandro Abasolo", "text_new": "{{short description|Mexican footballer}}\n{{Spanish name|Abasolo|Rodr\u00edguez}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Alejandro Abasolo \n| fullname = Alejandro Abasolo Rodr\u00edguez\n| image = \n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1997|7|13}}\n| birth_place = [[M\u00e9xico City]]\n| height = {{height|m=1.69}}\n| position = [[Midfielder]]\n| currentclub = [[Guadalupe F.C.|Guadalupe]] \n| clubnumber = \n| youthyears1 = 2012\n| youthclubs1 = [[Puebla FC|Puebla]]\n| youthyears2 = 2015\u20132016\n| youthclubs2 = [[Alebrijes de Oaxaca]]\n| years1 = 2016\u2013\n| clubs1 = [[Alebrijes de Oaxaca]]\n| caps1 = 0\n| goals1 = 0\n| years2 = 2016\u20132017\n| clubs2 = \u2192 [[Bel\u00e9n F.C.|Bel\u00e9n]] (loan)\n| caps2 = 4\n| goals2 = 0\n| years3 = 2019\u2013\n| clubs3 = \u2192 [[Guadalupe F.C.|Guadalupe]] (loan)\n| caps3 = 1\n| goals3 = 0\n| club-update = May 1, 2019\n}}\n\n'''Alejandro Abasolo Rodr\u00edguez''' (born 13 July 1997) is a Mexican [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for [[Guadalupe F.C.]] on loan from [[Alebrijes de Oaxaca]]. <ref>{{cite web|title=Alejandro Abasolo Rodr\u00edguez|url=http://ligamx.net/cancha/jugador/91229/alejandro-abasolo-rodriguez|website=ligamx.net|accessdate=2 September 2017|language=es-MX}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Soccerway|alejandro-abasolo-rodriguez/410081}}\n*[https://mobile.twitter.com/abasolo97?lang=en Abasolo twitter]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Abasolo, Alejandro}}\n[[Category:1997 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Footballers from Mexico City]]\n[[Category:Mexican footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Alebrijes de Oaxaca players]]\n[[Category:Bel\u00e9n F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Guadalupe F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Liga FPD players]]\n[[Category:Mexican expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Mexican expatriate sportspeople in Costa Rica]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Costa Rica]]\n\n{{Mexico-footy-midfielder-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Mexican footballer}}\n{{Spanish name|Abasolo|Rodr\u00edguez}}\n{{Infobox football biography\n| name = Alejandro Abasolo \n| fullname = Alejandro Abasolo Rodr\u00edguez\n| image = \n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1997|7|13}}\n| birth_place = [[M\u00e9xico City]]\n| height = {{height|m=1.69}}\n| position = [[Midfielder]]\n| currentclub = [[Guadalupe F.C.]] \n| clubnumber = \n| youthyears1 = 2012\n| youthclubs1 = [[Puebla FC|Puebla]]\n| youthyears2 = 2015\u20132016\n| youthclubs2 = [[Alebrijes de Oaxaca]]\n| years1 = 2016\u2013\n| clubs1 = [[Alebrijes de Oaxaca]]\n| caps1 = 0\n| goals1 = 0\n| years2 = 2016\u20132017\n| clubs2 = \u2192[[Bel\u00e9n F.C.|Bel\u00e9n]](loan)\n| caps2 = 4\n| goals2 = 0\n| years3 = 2019\u2013\n| clubs3 = \u2192[[Guadalupe F.C.]](loan\n| caps3 = 1\n| goals3 = 0\n| club-update = May 1, 2019\n}}\n\n'''Alejandro Abasolo Rodr\u00edguez''' (born 13 July 1997) is a Mexican [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[midfielder]] for [[Guadalupe F.C.]] on loan from [[Alebrijes de Oaxaca]]. <ref>{{cite web|title=Alejandro Abasolo Rodr\u00edguez|url=http://ligamx.net/cancha/jugador/91229/alejandro-abasolo-rodriguez|website=ligamx.net|accessdate=2 September 2017|language=es-MX}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*{{Soccerway|alejandro-abasolo-rodriguez/410081}}\n*[https://mobile.twitter.com/abasolo97?lang=en Abasolo twitter]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Abasolo, Alejandro}}\n[[Category:1997 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Footballers from Mexico City]]\n[[Category:Mexican footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Alebrijes de Oaxaca players]]\n[[Category:Bel\u00e9n F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Guadalupe F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Liga FPD players]]\n[[Category:Mexican expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Mexican expatriate sportspeople in Costa Rica]]\n[[Category:Expatriate footballers in Costa 