gh {{goal|36}}\n|stadium    = [[Thrissur Municipal Corporation Stadium|Municipal Corporation Stadium]]\n|location   = [[Thrissur]]\n|attendance = \n|referee    = \n}}\n\n===Group Y===\n{{#invoke:Sports table|main|style=WDL\n<!--Do not forget to update date or use ''complete'' without quotes when tournament is over-->\n|source=\n|team1=MH |team2=GO |team3=PB |team4=TN\n|result1=KO |result2=KO\n\n|win_MH=2 |draw_MH=1 |loss_MH=0 |gf_MH=7 |ga_MH=1\n|win_GO=1 |draw_GO=2 |loss_GO=0 |gf_GO=6 |ga_GO=3\n|win_PB=0 |draw_PB=2 |loss_PB=1 |gf_PB=3 |ga_PB=5\n|win_TN=0 |draw_TN=1 |loss_TN=2 |gf_TN=1 |ga_TN=8\n\n|name_MH=[[Maharashtra football team|Maharashtra]]\n|name_GO=[[Goa football team|Goa]]\n|name_PB=[[Punjab football team|Punjab]]\n|name_TN=[[Tamil Nadu football team|Tamil Nadu]]\n\n<!--Qualification and relegation column definitions-->\n|res_col_header=Q\n|col_KO=#ccffcc |text_KO=Advance to [[#Semi-finals|Semi-finals]]\n\n|class_rules = 1) points; 2) goal difference; 3) goals scored; 4) head-to-head result.\n}}\n{{Football box collapsible\n|date       = {{Start date|2000|04|09|df=y}}\n|time       = \n|team1      = [[Tamil Nadu football team|Tamil Nadu]]\n|score      = 1\u20131\n|report     = [http://www.thehindu.com/thehindu/2000/04/10/stories/07100447.htm Report]\n|team2      = [[Punjab football team|Punjab]]\n|goals1     = [[Syed Sabir Pasha|Pasha]] {{goal|79}}\n|goals2     = Sukhjit Singh {{goal|90}}\n|stadium    = [[Thrissur Municipal Corporation Stadium|Municipal Corporation Stadium]]\n|location   = [[Thrissur]]\n|attendance = \n|referee    = \n}}\n{{Football box collapsible\n|date       = {{Start date|2000|04|11|df=y}}\n|time       = \n|team1      = [[Tamil Nadu football team|Tamil Nadu]]\n|score      = 0\u20134\n|report     = [http://www.thehindu.com/thehindu/2000/04/12/stories/07120447.htm Report]\n|team2      = [[Maharashtra football team|Maharashtra]]\n|goals1     =\n|goals2     = Mohammed Najeeb {{goal|2}}<br/>[[Khalid Jamil|Jamil]] {{goal|8}}<br/>Khalid Siddiqu